                <div class="field field-name-field-pg-slider-title field-type-text field-label-hidden">
                 <div class="field-items">
                  <div class="field-item even">
                   Research Resource Program (RRP)
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field field-name-field-pg-slider-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
                 <div class="field-items">
                  <div class="field-item even">
                   Provides strategic planning and implementation of programs to support core facilities and other research resources. Also provides administrative, operational and financial management tools and support to core facilities.
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field field-name-field-pg-slider-link field-type-link-field field-label-hidden">
